question.value:
There are two manipulated variables. They are:

- the order in which the participants are trained in the two methods (in particular, which method they receive training in at stage 1, either the ODNI method or the RST);

- which version of each product the participant evaluates ('default', 'poorly written' or 'well-written').

See the following two files, attached:

- a description of our model and rationale for choosing it;
- the R script that will be used to fit it and perform hypothesis tests.

